      "side": 1,
      "message": "yeah, go/filtering is especially relevant to SQL databases, because you can directly map a go/filtering expression to a SQL expression. I support go/filtering format for this MDB. If you write or port the parser, we\u0027d reuse it in buildbucket v2. See partial parsers internally.",
